@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ectkuf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.exp((v1 + 1.00 - v1 + 0.20)))
    v1 = (tmp + (v1 - wp.abs(v0 + 0.25)))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.abs(wp.exp(v2 + 0.98)))
    v2 = ((0.07 - (tmp + 0.24 / v2 + 0.49)) - (wp.exp(v1 + 0.96) / tmp))
    v0 = wp.abs(0.57)
    data[tid] = v0
